import {
    cyclope_eye,
    play_icon,
    arrow_right,
    bg_android,
    bg_blue,
    bg_blue2,
    bg_dote,
    bg_fear,
    bg_hantu,
    bg_hantu2,
    bg_red,
    char_ca_map,
    char_cho_muc,
    char_dote,
    char_giap,
    char_hantu,
    char_legend,
    char_milo,
    char_sep,
    char_simon,
    char_that,
    dote_poster1,
    dote_poster2,
    hantu_poster1,
    hantu_poster2,
    kid_poster1,
    kid_poster2,
    poster_android,
    poster_cho_muc,
    poster_dote,
    poster_hanto,
    poster_kid,
    poster_sep,
    poster_simon_vu,
    productaion_banner,
    sep_poster1,
    sep_poster2,
    sep_poster3,
    sep_poster4,
    tab_camap,
    tab_chomuc,
    tab_dote,
    tab_legends,
    tab_milo,
    tab_sep,
    tab_simon,
    tab_hantu,
    tab_that,
    tab_thiet_giap,
    video_thumbnail1,
    video_thumbnail2,
    video_thumbnail3,
  } from '../../assets/images';
  
  import video from '../../assets/video/placeholder.mov';
  
  const sepData={
      ref:89,
      main_img:sep_main_img,
      placeholder:sep_placeholder,
      title_img:sep_title_img,
      release:['LIVE-ACTION MOVIE','2022'],
      para:'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Tempore officia magni distinctio neque hic, aliquam eius nisi ad sint reprehenderit saepe, temporibus, porro ex ea ut fugiat voluptates commodi molestiae.',
      videos:[
          {poster:video_thumbnail1,source:video},
          {poster:video_thumbnail2,source:video},
          {poster:video_thumbnail3,source:video},
      ],
  }
  
  const slides = [
      {id:0 ,img:tab_sep},
      {id:1 ,img:tab_simon},
      {id:2 ,img:tab_camap},
      {id:3 ,img:tab_dote},
      {id:4 ,img:tab_thiet_giap},
      {id:5 ,img:tab_hantu},
      {id:6 ,img:tab_that},
      {id:7 ,img:tab_legends},
      {id:8 ,img:tab_chomuc},
      {id:9 ,img:tab_milo},
      {id:10 ,img:tab_legends},
  
  ];
  
  const settings = {
      accessibility: true,
      arrows: false,
      dots: false,
      infinite: true,
      speed: 500,
      slidesToShow: 7,
      slidesToScroll: 1,
      focusOnSelect: true,
      className: "basic_slider",
      responsive: [
          {
            breakpoint: 1400,
            settings: {
              slidesToShow: 6,
              slidesToScroll: 1,
            }
          },
          {
            breakpoint: 1200,
            settings: {
              slidesToShow: 5,
              slidesToScroll: 1,
            }
          },
          {
            breakpoint: 991,
            settings: {
              slidesToShow: 4,
              slidesToScroll: 1,
            }
          },
          {
            breakpoint: 720,
            settings: {
              slidesToShow: 3,
              slidesToScroll: 1,
            }
          },
          {
            breakpoint: 500,
            settings: {
              slidesToShow: 2,
              slidesToScroll: 1,
            }
          },
      ]
  };
  
  export {
      slides,
      settings,
      sepData,
  };
